Package: APL
Type: Package
Title: Association Plots
Version: 0.99.0
Author: Clemens Kohl and Ela Gralinska
Maintainer: Clemens Kohl <kohl.clemens@gmail.com>
Description: This package performs Correspondence Analysis (CA) and allows to visualize the results in Association Plots (APL) and biplots. For an APL genes can be scored and gene enrichment run for further insights.
